text.tspan: Do not edit the Print at Home Tiling!
Arrange shapes efficiently using page tiling as reference.
Final pattern is broken into seperate pages with an automated script. Total document size must be in
increments of 7.5 x 10 inches. Document should not exceed 45 x 60 inches.
Final pattern will include letter/A4, tabloid/A4, and if necessary, large format / A0 paper sizes.
